WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Fire and Smoke Damage restoration involves complex cleaning and deodorising processes.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
Soot can be acidic and corrosive, requiring specialised cleaning agents and techniques.

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
Smoke odour removal often requires thermal fogging or ozone treatment.

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
RestoreAssist tracks all cleaning stages, chemical usage, and air quality readings.

00:32.000 --> 00:40.000
Generate complete restoration reports with before and after photos, scope of works, and recommended post-restoration actions.